version            1.3
categories         devel
platforms          darwin
maintainers        sean@sfarc.net mww
description	       GNU getopt library
long_description   GNU getopt library similar but more powerful than the \
                   standard getopt(3). It includes the GNU-style getopt_long() \
                   function.
